title: Bet on the late bloomers
author: VD
content_html: Over at Alpha Game, I consider the implications of a new study concerning the impact of starter sex on the statistical probability of divorce, while the resident omega explains the value of cold approaches even when they don’t appear to be getting him anywhere. And Susan Walsh explains why you don’t get two chances at an initial impression.
